1
00:01:39,519 --> 00:01:40,519
This commoner has one more item

2
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:42,319
that I risk losing my head

3
00:01:42,599 --> 00:01:43,599
to present to the Empress Dowager.

4
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,439
Preposterous!

5
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:04,120
How dare they forge my decree!

6
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:05,599
Please calm your anger, Empress Dowager.

7
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:06,680
Imperial Grandmother, please calm your anger.

8
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,240
Empress Dowager.

9
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,520
This secret letter and this forged decree

10
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:12,360
were all found in the All-Knowing Manor.

11
00:02:13,479 --> 00:02:14,879
That so-called Thousand-Mechanism Secret Treasure

12
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:17,240
contains not only the forged decree in your hand,

13
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,560
but also edicts for appointing officials,

14
00:02:20,039 --> 00:02:22,439
secret correspondence between ministries and offices,

15
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:24,439
defense maps of border garrisons,

16
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:28,240
weapon blueprints, salt and iron receipts, and tax ledgers.

17
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,599
A cursory glance by this commoner

18
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:31,960
was enough to make me shudder.

19
00:02:32,599 --> 00:02:35,400
It is as if the court is not in the Throne Room,

20
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,599
but in the All-Knowing Manor.

21
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:40,759
Imperial Grandmother.

22
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:43,599
This All-Knowing Manor is a Jianghu sect.

23
00:02:44,479 --> 00:02:46,080
If there were no power in the court backing it,

24
00:02:46,639 --> 00:02:48,080
they certainly would not possess such items.

25
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:50,439
Such rebellious subjects and traitors—

26
00:02:50,919 --> 00:02:52,039
if not rooted out immediately,

27
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:53,599
I fear they will...

28
00:02:53,719 --> 00:02:54,759
Alarmist talk!

29
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,560
Your Highness, Crown Prince.

30
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:59,840
Do not spout nonsense before the Empress Dowager.

31
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,199
Whether it is nonsense or not,

32
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,400
an investigation will reveal.

33
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:05,000
I ask Imperial Grandmother to make a decision soon.

34
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:05,879
Empress Dowager.

35
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:08,120
The Emperor is critically ill right now.

36
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,800
If this matter is blown out of proportion,

37
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:12,520
I fear the court will become unstable.

38
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:14,199
Father Emperor is bedridden,

39
00:03:14,439 --> 00:03:15,840
but Imperial Grandmother is here to take charge.

40
00:03:16,719 --> 00:03:17,800
Eunuch Liu, by saying this,

41
00:03:18,199 --> 00:03:20,280
where do you place Imperial Grandmother's authority?

42
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,599
Shut up, all of you!

43
00:03:23,759 --> 00:03:24,759
In your opinion,

44
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,800
who in the court is suspicious?

45
00:03:27,719 --> 00:03:28,520
This commoner believes

46
00:03:29,199 --> 00:03:30,280
that within the court, there must be

47
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:31,919
spies from the Desert Kingdom.

48
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:34,039
The Desert Kingdom repeatedly violates our borders.

49
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:35,439
The frontline has just finished fighting.

50
00:03:35,879 --> 00:03:38,199
Then such a disaster occurs at the All-Knowing Manor.

51
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,639
The officials involved also lost their lives because of it.

52
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:43,479
It is clear someone wants to use the Emperor's illness

53
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,039
to shake the foundation of our dynasty.

54
00:03:45,719 --> 00:03:46,719
Apart from the Desert Kingdom,

55
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,319
this commoner truly cannot think of

56
00:03:48,759 --> 00:03:50,680
who else would be so audacious.

57
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:52,240
Then tell me,

58
00:03:52,919 --> 00:03:54,319
why did they want to harm the Capital Governor?

59
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,479
Only when those in the scheme die

60
00:03:56,719 --> 00:03:58,759
can the schemer live.

61
00:03:59,439 --> 00:04:00,479
Do you know

62
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:03,759
that speaking wrongly can cost you your head?

63
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,960
This commoner speaks not a word in jest.

64
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,319
I beg the Empress Dowager to allow this commoner

65
00:04:08,439 --> 00:04:09,479
to return to the All-Knowing Manor

66
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,280
to thoroughly investigate the Desert Kingdom forces behind this

67
00:04:11,919 --> 00:04:13,120
and give the court an explanation.

68
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,759
Audacious scoundrel!

69
00:04:15,159 --> 00:04:16,639
Do not be insolent before the Empress Dowager!

70
00:04:17,879 --> 00:04:18,879
Empress Dowager, this old slave believes...

71
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:20,720
When can you give me a result?

72
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:22,439
Five days.

73
00:04:22,839 --> 00:04:23,720
Good.

74
00:04:26,519 --> 00:04:27,600
Then I

75
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:30,199
shall await your good news.

76
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,920
Escorting a felon

77
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:41,839
without even searching him?

78
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,240
Go back and tell your superior,

79
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:46,079
the Dark Inspection Division does not feed useless waste.

80
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,600
Let's go, Little Eunuch Liu.

81
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:55,759
We are in a hurry.

82
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,720
Everyone, look!

83
00:05:15,879 --> 00:05:17,399
That rider is a Desert Kingdom spy!

84
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:18,480
Don't let him escape!

85
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,279
Stop him!

86
00:05:19,839 --> 00:05:21,480
Quick, stop him! Stop him!

87
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,399
Don't let him get away!

88
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,079
Get out of the way!

89
00:05:24,279 --> 00:05:25,319
Dark Inspection Division business!

90
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,240
All of you, get out of the way!

91
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:27,120
Hit him, quick!

92
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:28,279
Beat him to death!

93
00:05:28,439 --> 00:05:28,879
Hit him!

94
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,000
Hit him!

95
00:05:31,639 --> 00:05:32,560
Don't let him escape!

96
00:05:32,759 --> 00:05:33,399
Beat him to death!

97
00:05:34,519 --> 00:05:35,040
Hit him!

98
00:05:37,399 --> 00:05:37,879
Young Master Ye!

99
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:38,800
Go!

100
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,519
Trying to run?

101
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:53,800
Let's go.

102
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:04,560
Master Ye.

103
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:05,879
Do you remember me?

104
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,120
I do.

105
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,199
Master Kun sent a message long ago.

106
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,600
To have the Dali Temple keep you here.

107
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:11,759
And ensure your safety at all costs.

108
00:06:12,399 --> 00:06:13,079
Thank you for the trouble.

109
00:06:16,319 --> 00:06:18,000
These four brothers are here to protect you.

110
00:06:18,519 --> 00:06:19,759
We have prepared a residence for you.

111
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,600
No one will find you there.

112
00:06:22,879 --> 00:06:23,399
No.

113
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:24,920
I must return to All-Knowing Manor.

114
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,439
We went through so much trouble to rescue you.

115
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,560
Why do you want to go back?

116
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:31,199
Master Kun and the others are still at the Manor.

117
00:06:31,879 --> 00:06:32,680
I have to go back and save them.

118
00:06:36,399 --> 00:06:37,079
Alright.

119
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:38,600
Since you are going back,

120
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:39,839
We will go with you.

121
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,319
Go prepare a carriage.

122
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:41,959
Yes.

123
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:44,720
The Dark Inspection Division has received the news.

124
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,839
They will surely seal the city gates.

125
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:47,959
Let's leave first.

126
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,199
Okay.

127
00:06:55,279 --> 00:06:56,120
Empress Dowager.

128
00:06:56,399 --> 00:06:57,199
Eunuch Li.

129
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,600
Imperial Grandmother is resting.

130
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,360
Keep your voice down.

131
00:07:03,319 --> 00:07:04,199
Don't disturb Her Majesty.

132
00:07:05,399 --> 00:07:05,800
By the way,

133
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,120
I haven't had time to thank you, Eunuch Li.

134
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,240
That batch of poison-repelling pills you collected,

135
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,120
I have graciously accepted them.

136
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,120
What of the Crown Prince?

137
00:07:30,439 --> 00:07:31,879
And what of the Empress Dowager?

138
00:07:32,519 --> 00:07:34,079
Once the Emperor passes away,

139
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:36,240
The whole world will be mine.

140
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:41,639
Once I control the entire court,

141
00:07:42,319 --> 00:07:46,560
You will all be buried with the Emperor.

142
00:08:40,519 --> 00:08:41,000
You seek death!

143
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:41,600
Stop!

144
00:08:46,639 --> 00:08:47,679
Are you alright, little girl?

145
00:08:48,679 --> 00:08:49,159
Get up.

146
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,519
Are you lost?

147
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:03,840
Give her some money.

148
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,080
I don't want money.

149
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,399
Where are your parents?

150
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,320
Any other family?

151
00:09:16,159 --> 00:09:16,720
Manor Lord.

152
00:09:17,159 --> 00:09:18,440
Didn't you want to find a maid

153
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,440
to serve the Eldest Miss?

154
00:09:19,799 --> 00:09:21,440
This girl looks like an orphan.

155
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,639
She is the perfect candidate.

156
00:09:39,759 --> 00:09:40,480
Xiao Bai.

157
00:09:42,039 --> 00:09:42,480
Xiao Bai.

158
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,080
Ye Li.

159
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,639
Didn't I tell you not to come back?

160
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:56,679
I said I would come back to save you.

161
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,399
They didn't give you trouble, did they?

162
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,960
Where are those people now?

163
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,440
They are in the main hall.

164
00:10:12,799 --> 00:10:13,440
Ye Li.

165
00:10:14,639 --> 00:10:15,679
You shouldn't have come back.

166
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,120
Don't worry.

167
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:20,279
This time,

168
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,200
I brought back experts from the Dali Temple.

169
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:24,519
We will definitely get out.

170
00:10:30,159 --> 00:10:30,919
Xiao Bai.

171
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,480
There is something

172
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,440
I've always wanted to ask you.

173
00:10:40,799 --> 00:10:41,360
You...

174
00:10:42,559 --> 00:10:43,440
Are you...

175
00:10:43,759 --> 00:10:44,399
I am not.

176
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,559
I haven't finished speaking.

177
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,320
I know what you want to say.

178
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:51,720
I am not.

179
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,279
Xiao Bai.

180
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:03,600
Tell me.

181
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,759
Would Zhaoyun kill someone?
